== About me
I am a postdoctoral fellow at The Chinese University of Hone Kong under the supervision of Prof. [https://sites.google.com/view/academicyuechen/home Yue Chen] (2022-present).\n
I received my PhD degree from the [https://www.eea.tsinghua.edu.cn Department of Electrical Engineering] at [https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn Tsinghua University] under the supervision of Prof. [https://www.eea.tsinghua.edu.cn/faculties/qlu.htm Qiang Lu] (2017-2022).\n
I received the B.E. degree in electrical engineering and B.S. degree in mathematics from Tsinghua University (2013-2017).\n

I am a postdoctoral fellow at The Chinese University of Hone Kong under the supervision of Prof. [https://sites.google.com/view/academicyuechen/home Yue Chen] (2022-present).\n
I received my PhD degree from the [https://www.ji.sjtu.edu.cn University of Michigan - Shanghai Jiao Tong University Joint Institute] at [https://www.sjtu.edu.cn Shanghai Jiao Tong University] under the supervision of Prof. Chengbin Ma (2017-2021).\n
I received the M.S. degree and B.E. degree in vehicle engineering from China Agricultural University (2014-2016, and 2010-2014).\n

== Research interests
- Theory: optimization, game theory, control, and deep reinforcement learning
- Applications: electric vehicle charging stations integrated with renewables and energy storages, shared energy storage, microgrids, smart grids.
